      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775122186626,
      "link": null,
      "text": "Key = exact request (URL, params, headers)    Value = full computed response\nHIT = skip ALL computation (zero cost, instant)    MISS = full compute + store\nExamples: Browser cache, CDN (Cloudflare), Redis, Memcached",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "wc_230",
      "originalText": "Key = exact request (URL, params, headers)    Value = full computed response\nHIT = skip ALL computation (zero cost, instant)    MISS = full compute + store\nExamples: Browser cache, CDN (Cloudflare), Redis, Memcached",
